API Reference

RESTful API for integrating FlashFusion into your applications

Quick Start

Base URL

https://api.flashfusion.co/v1

Authentication

Authorization: Bearer <your_api_key>
Content-Type: application/json

Example Request

curl -X POST https://api.flashfusion.co/v1/generate/code \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_API_KEY" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "description": "Create a React component for a user profile card",
    "framework": "react",
    "language": "typescript"
  }'

API Endpoints

Authentication

POST/auth/login

Authenticate user and receive access token

POST/auth/register

Create a new user account

POST/auth/refresh

Refresh expired access token

POST/auth/logout

Invalidate current session

Projects

GET/projects

List all projects for authenticated user

POST/projects

Create a new project

GET/projects/:id

Get project details by ID

PATCH/projects/:id

Update project information

DELETE/projects/:id

Delete a project

Code Generation

POST/generate/code

Generate code based on description

POST/generate/component

Generate UI component

POST/generate/api

Generate API endpoints

GET/generate/history

Get generation history

Deployments

POST/deploy

Deploy project to platform

GET/deploy/:id/status

Check deployment status

GET/deploy/:id/logs

Get deployment logs

POST/deploy/:id/rollback

Rollback to previous version
